---
title: Easy Garlic & Herb Lamb Burger with Wedges, Caramelised Onion & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Did someone say they ordered a burger and fries? Because we have something a little better than that. How about a lamb burger
infused with garlic and herbs, balanced with sweet caramelised onion. Can’t get enough of that herby taste, well this burger has a
layer of our dill-parsley mayo ready to go. Of course we can’t forget the fries, but let’s upgrade it to crispy potato wedges because who
doesn’t love wedges? Order up!

